title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 - Nov 24 2021
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 - Nov 24 2021
description:
Fauci accuses Tucker Carlson of killing people by "weaponizing lies." EIB's very own James “Bo Snerdley” Golden joins the show to reminisce about working with the legend, Rush Limbaugh, and how much Thanksgiving meant to Rush and to all of us. CBS tells audience to give covid tests to Thanksgiving guests. C&B review classic Thanksgiving movies and remember Thanksgivings past.
